## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in subjective interpretations of childhood and adulthood. The perspectives gathered are primarily from online articles and essays, which may not encompass the full range of academic research on the topic. Additionally, cultural and individual differences in the experience of childhood and adulthood are not extensively covered in this report.